Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: gitbasher
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, bash (>= 4.0), git (>= 2.23), sed, grep, coreutils
Recommends: curl
Description: Simple bash utility that makes git easy to use
 gitbasher is a wrapper around the most used git commands with a cleaner
 interface. It helps speed up the development process, making it more
 consistent and reducing mistakes.
 .
 Features:
  - Intuitive command interface
  - AI-powered commit messages
  - Branch management
  - Interactive rebasing and merging
  - Commit message templates
  - Tag management
  - Stash management
  - Git hooks
